{"tid":2425164,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有屋企人會屌你叫外賣","createTime":"2021-02-27T07:07:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T03:39:12.000Z","uid":14786,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"178bc9ae650855637b0adee6f736fdc8b1c4fd00","tid":2425164,"uid":14786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"返左五日工<br />\n星期六/日唔想落街<br />\n間唔中叫一次有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話咩寧願自己行<br />\n我叫親都問我幾錢<br />\n然後比說話我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n    而家D人真係有錢......<br />\n    後生仔慳返啲錢啦......<br />\n 乜乜77<br />\n心諗幾廿蚊我買股票手續費都冇左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時真係想同佢兩個講<br />\n你地後生係咁慳<br />\n點解我係住公屋嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2946e133358be0194f80c2c34eb94247652a28","tid":2425164,"uid":123053,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"住公屋唔駛忍<br />\n大大聲屌7佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84334590bf7429d85341bba4886cd08bdf46342","tid":2425164,"uid":50101,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"大撚把，做 fuckpanda送上樓，每十個都總有一兩個會俾佢老母話佢嘥撚哂D錢乜乜柒柒，如果係老麥雞記之類佢認為係冇益嘅食物就更加大反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老母都係為你好之嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85752a5e580a62af78d7d4ac05e52be8317793af","tid":2425164,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"死廢老<br />\n呢啲錢就識慳 <br />\n買餸 煮飯 洗碗 唔係時間嚟? 無機會成本?"},{"pid":"61e006e5bb9973ab20028946fa5320ebc71d8b55","tid":2425164,"uid":92789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"屋企人話你都算&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n最搞笑係我去餐廳拎外賣，個老闆娘屌啲人用外賣平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢話啲人食米唔知米貴！自己落黎拎咪唔洗畀人賺運輸費囉！個餐又會平啲！"},{"pid":"040e8dcb29c044b59b481e700341b15a2e5384c7","tid":2425164,"uid":14786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"佢仲話叫我比錢佢佢去買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我心諗<br />\n人地用電單車直接車過嚟<br />\n杯熱奶茶到我手係仲熱辣辣架囉<br />\n你搭巴士出去買<br />\n來回連埋排隊起碼都9個字<br />\n咩都凍晒啦"},{"pid":"6beea6ae0c5806e6662aac14a22b1d783eabc41f","tid":2425164,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T18:33:01.000Z","msg":"多數d 老豆老母都會叫你慳d 洗<br />\n乜都要慳。凍飲加三蚊都講下<br />\n<br />\n但係又唔見得佢地儲到幾多錢<br />\n仲要試過幾次比人呃。差銀行十幾廿萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n串番佢地當堂駁唔到"},{"pid":"807c49c688806814aee0b8319bfbbc72b0b6b479","tid":2425164,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T03:39:12.000Z","msg":"就係慳先住公屋<br />\n<br />\n應使得使囉<br />\n我見我父母慳黎唔知做咩，用又唔敢用<br />\n咩享受都無<br />\n因為有積蓄老人金又拎唔到高額<br />\n外父母就用晒佢，又旅行又食好野<br />\n拎最高額老人金<br />\n慳來唔知有咩用咁"}]}